        <h4>Filing & Representation</h4>
        <p>Our advocate files the case, handles court appearances, and keeps you updated at every stage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="num">5</div>
        <h4>Resolution</h4>
        <p>Whether through settlement or judgment, we ensure you get the best possible outcome.</p>
